gems.name: google-analytics-admin-v1alpha
gems.info: The Analytics Admin API allows for programmatic access to the Google Analytics App+Web configuration data. You can use the Google Analytics Admin API to manage accounts and App+Web properties. Note that google-analytics-admin-v1alpha is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-analytics-admin instead. See the readme for more details.
